data.title: 800 5th Ave 10D, New York, NY, 10065
data.meta_description: 800 5th Ave 10D, New York, NY, 10065 is a Rental in Upper East Side, New York that is listed for rent at $11,400. This is a 2 BR, 2 bath, 1430 sq ft property.
data.text:
Central Park at your doorstep! This split two bedroom/two bathroom has a marble dining foyer, oak strip flooring, and great afternoon light overlooking the Park.

Welcome to 800 Fifth Avenue, an exclusive 33 story tower consisting of expansive one-, two-, three- and four-bedroom residences in an unmatched location – directly overlooking Manhattan’s famed Central Park. 800 Fifth Avenue offers residents one of the most unique living experiences not only in New York City, but possibly the world, with panoramic views of the park, close proximity to both Madison Avenue and Fifth Avenue shopping and easy access to multiple subway lines.
